<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Copliot on UNO's Page</title><link>https://sleepman9.github.io/tags/copliot/</link><description>Recent content in Copliot on UNO's Page</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://sleepman9.github.io/tags/copliot/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Tools Trick</title><link>https://sleepman9.github.io/p/tools-trick/</link><pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://sleepman9.github.io/p/tools-trick/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://sleepman9.github.io/p/tools-trick/cover.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Tools Trick" />&lt;h2 id="1-vscode中github-copilot在ssh远程环境中无法登录问题">1. VSCode中Github Copilot在SSH远程环境中无法登录问题
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="1-在vs-code中按f1键调出命令行输入settingsjson选择远程环境中的配置文件">1. 在VS Code中，按F1键调出命令行，输入settings.json，选择远程环境中的配置文件：
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://sleepman9.github.io/p/tools-trick/asserts/copliot.png"
width="825"
height="502"
srcset="https://sleepman9.github.io/p/tools-trick/asserts/copliot_hu_d04c34523884441.png 480w, https://sleepman9.github.io/p/tools-trick/asserts/copliot_hu_f6631b22a2511959.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
alt="alt text"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="164"
data-flex-basis="394px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="2-添加如下配置">2. 添加如下配置：
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;remote.extensionKind&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;GitHub.copilot&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;ui&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">],&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;GitHub.copilot-chat&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;ui&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">],&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="3-重启vs-code即可">3. 重启VS Code即可。
